<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，寇夫人很早就跑到了官府。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她眼里含着泪水，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>告诉官府大人说自己前一天撒了谎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“唐僧和他的徒弟们是清白的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇夫人抽泣着说，“求您放了他们吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>官府大人点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我正准备今天早上要放了他们呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他说了昨天晚上游魂来访的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇夫人大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我丈夫昨天晚上来找我了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们得马上放了他们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们马上去了唐僧的大牢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个看守打开了牢门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从那里出来，真好。”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是。”八戒打着哈欠说，“床太不舒服。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇夫人低头向唐僧行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我说你杀了我丈夫，陷害了你。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请原谅我。我做了件错的事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对！”悟空喊道，“那样做确实很不对！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧把手放在悟空的肩膀上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别喊，悟空。”他看了看寇夫人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们原谅你。寇员外是好人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的死是可怕的悲剧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空摸了摸下巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也许可以救活他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇夫人和官府大人吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你真的可以吗？”寇夫人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧笑了。“是的，悟空可以。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空救活过乌鸡国的国王。”他看了看悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那时候太上老君帮了你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你又要找他帮忙吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不。”悟空说，“太上老君不太喜欢我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要去幽冥界跟阎王说。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空一走进阎王殿，阎王就皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么来了，悟空？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174958</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你从生死簿上划掉了自己的名字，已经不会死了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174958</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。“我还想你是不是还记得那件事呢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我是来找寇员外的名字的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“寇员外？”阎王打开生死簿，翻了几页。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊，对，他两天前死了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在他在大愿菩萨那里呢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那地方也在幽冥界。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空去找大愿菩萨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好啊，悟空。”大愿菩萨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您好，大愿菩萨。”悟空问候道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“两天前我的朋友寇员外被杀来到了这里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想把他重新带回人间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大愿菩萨扬起了一边的眉毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你想救活他？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”悟空说，“我在保护唐僧去西天取真经。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇员外对我们非常好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大愿菩萨笑了。“好。寇员外可以回到人间，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到了他该回来的时候，他可以再回到这里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大愿菩萨把悟空带到一个屋内。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇员外正坐在大桌子前，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在看书简，脸上挂着微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到悟空时，眼睛一亮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“见到你很高兴，悟空！”寇员外说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在这儿干什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有一个好消息。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的寿命还没有结束。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要把你带回人间。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇员外看上去有些疑惑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着大愿菩萨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大愿菩萨点了一下头。“你可以回人间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等你寿命结束后，你可以再回到这里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310016</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>寇员外从桌子后跑出来，低头行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢您，大愿菩萨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然我在这里也很幸福，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但我也很想见到我的妻子和朋友们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空走近寇员外。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你马上就会回家的，员外。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空念了一个咒语，寇员外消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>